Note on APQC PCF Framework:

The APQC Process Classification Framework (PCF) is a product of APQC
(American Productivity & Quality Center). The PLE Governance Process Standard
is an independent adaptation and extension of the PCF taxonomy concepts for
post-labor governance contexts. This work is not affiliated with or endorsed
by APQC. For the original PCF framework, visit https://www.apqc.org/pcf.
